releases.name: Pokemon Go v2.0.0
releases.body:
# What You Will See
- Basic profile information
  - Team
  - Level Progress
  - Kilometers walked
  - Egg Incubator Progress
- Your Pokemon
  - Includes overall IV % as well as ATK/DEF/STA individual values
  - Sort by IV, CP, Favorites, Name, Type, and Recent

# Behind the scenes
- Changed API backend
- Cleaned up a lot of code

releases.name: Pokemon Go v1.1.0
releases.body: - Updated to work with Niantic's new API changes

releases.name: Pokemon Go v1.0.0
releases.body:
- Fixed issue with search area showing things far away, but missing some right next to you
- Made Windows binaries smaller (hopefully less time to extract)
- Promoted to major release

releases.name: Pokemon Go v0.4.1
releases.body: - Fixed geocoding issue with default location if Chrome is unable to detect your current location

releases.name: Pokemon Go v0.4.0
releases.body:
- Added Journal to see items & caught pokemon
- Added ability to "spin" pokestops

releases.name: Pokemon Go v0.3.0
releases.body:
- added walking/running/driving/teleport options for moving around the map
- Replaced circle with avatar
- fixed bug with displaying pokestop/gym information
- fixed bug with not showing pokemon/pokestops/gyms while walking

releases.name: Pokemon Go v0.3.0 (Alpha Release)
releases.body:
This is an **alpha** release.  It has been tested, but not a whole lot.
- Added directions in and the option to walk/drive/teleport to locations
  - useful for egg hatching
  - teleporting everywhere may get you a temporary ban

releases.name: Pokemon Go Beta v0.2.0
releases.body:
- Added search box for places
- Added pokestop & gym names
- fix minor bugs

releases.name: Pokemon Go Beta v0.1.1
releases.body:
- Added Pokemon info inside lure pokestop instead of on top of
- Fixed marker overlay "flashing" issue on map
- Fixed issue with locations not showing up in certain areas of the world

releases.name: Pokemon Go Beta v0.1.0
releases.body:
## v0.1.0
- Added pokestops and gyms
- Show details about all markers on the map when clicked
- Fixed some Windows build issues.
